# Network Configuration
ALCHEMY_API_KEY=""
# Deployer wallet private key (no 0x prefix or with 0x). KEEP SECRET.
DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY=""

# Etherscan V2 API (for contract verification)
# https://etherscan.io/apis
ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=""

# ===========================================
# Grid Contract Deployment
# ===========================================
# USDC: Required. Your test USDC or mainnet USDC token address (e.g. Base USDC).
USDC=""

# GRID_ORACLE: Address allowed to call GridBank.reportReading(). Leave empty to use deployer.
GRID_ORACLE=""

# Network-Specific Settings
MAINNET_FORKING_ENABLED="false"

# ===========================================
# Quick Start (Deploy: AgentTreasury, ReputationRegistry, GridBank, VWAPDemo)
# ===========================================
# 1. cp .env.example .env
# 2. Set ALCHEMY_API_KEY, DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY, ETHERSCAN_API_KEY
# 3. Set USDC (required for GridBank). Optionally set GRID_ORACLE (defaults to deployer).
# 4. Deploy: npx hardhat deploy --network baseSepolia
# 5. Verify: npx hardhat run scripts/verify.ts --network baseSepolia
